title: Episode 158: The Dutch Oven (Feat. J Prince)
itunes:title: Episode 158: The Dutch Oven (Feat. J Prince)
description:
J Prince joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and takes you to school! He opens up about his past relationships and how it has evolved him into the man he is today. J Prince shares insight and advice regarding many situations you may find yourself in, concerning your relationship. Enjoy!
